options.content: Diagnosi - Estat de les tramitacions

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  daterequested
FROM
  gavius
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(daterequested)

SELECT
  ssascscl0name,
  (select count(*) from llenos where status = 'Evaluating' and llenos.ssascscl0name = gavius.ssascscl0name and $__timeFilter(daterequested)) as en_curs,
  (select count(*) from llenos where status = 'Approved' and llenos.ssascscl0name = gavius.ssascscl0name and $__timeFilter(daterequested)) as favorables,
  (select count(*) from llenos where status = 'Denied' and llenos.ssascscl0name = gavius.ssascscl0name and $__timeFilter(daterequested)) as desfavorables
FROM gavius
GROUP BY socialaidsocialaid_id, ssascscl0name
ORDER BY socialaidsocialaid_id

SELECT
  count(*) as ExclusioResidencial
FROM gavius
WHERE
socialaidsocialaid_id = 1 and
  $__timeFilter(daterequested)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  date_trunc('month',daterequested) as time,
  count(*) AS "favorables"
FROM llenos
WHERE
  status = 'Approved' and
  $__timeFilter(daterequested)
GROUP BY date_trunc('month',daterequested)
ORDER BY date_trunc('month',daterequested)
